  m_Name: ModeConfigurationProductiveDomestic
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  BehaviourMode: 3
  ModeContext: In this mode, the user is focused on home/domestic tasks. These can
    include things such as grocery shopping, home maintainance, taking out the trash,
    fixing a vehicle, and other chores/errands and life-obligations-related tasks.
  PersonalityAdditions: Remind the user that a well maintained home lowers the user's
    stress. Grocery shopping helps prevent spending extra money eating out. Maintanance
    reduces the risk of emergency expenses. Maintaining cleanliness is good for health
    and stress.
  ResponseInstructionAdditionsAllModes: 
  ProactiveLoopbackTimeMinutes: 30
